{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/Intergalacto.png?t=1731433671\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into the diverse world of &quot;Intergalacto-1,&quot; where every mode offers a unique adventure! Each mode is designed for endless excitement and challenges.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/mystic_townn.png?t=1731433671\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the eerie horror mode, <i>Mystic Town: The Abyss</i>, you\u2019ll face an invisible ghost and many magical dangers lurking around every corner. As you explore the creepy town, you\u2019ll need to collect clues and keys to unlock doors and find your way out. Everything that happens here is connected, and every choice you make will test your wits and bravery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This mode has been carefully polished for the best experience, with smooth gameplay and stunning visuals.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/pog.gif?t=1731433671\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Warzone mode is a multiplayer arena where you can create or join servers, play with friends, and enjoy intense battles. Team up or go solo as you fight through waves of enemies and obstacles in a quest for victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/pog.gif?t=1731433671\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Battle of Lives mode, you'll collect keys by fighting guards to unlock doors that teleport you to different challenges. Some doors lead to the boss level, while others take you to zombie mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/pog.gif?t=1731433671\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ultimate challenge is facing off against the nearly unbeatable boss, INM. With only a slim chance of victory, will you dare to take on this formidable foe? Conquer INM in the Battle of Lives mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/pog.gif?t=1731433671\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Finally, in zombie mode, you'll face waves of undead that become more difficult with each round. Access this mode through the doors in Battle of Lives, testing your survival skills to the limit. Fight off the relentless horde and see how long you can endure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an epic journey through the cosmos in &quot;Intergalacto-1,&quot; where every triumph brings you one step closer to uncovering the secrets of the universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/extras/output-onlinegiftools.gif?t=1731433671\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Cosmic Champion","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2990800/59e02ea8230bbf0e0560cff328d7e42caed4aa92.jpg"},{"name":"Persistent","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2990800/fc6342a39374238d0640ac3403859dacfd4ec1e7.jpg"}],"total":2},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731433671","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2990800/page.bg.jpg?t=1731433671","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_as